front.title: •Blaster Proficiency
front.gametext: USED: If you just targeted with a blaster, add 3 to your weapon destiny.  LOST: Lose 1 Force to cause one opponent's character just 'hit' to be immediately placed in Lost Pile. OR Cancel Levitation Attack.
front.lore: Some people think that hokey religions and ancient weapons are no match for a good blaster at your side.
